<dt class='comment-author blog-author' id='c6883176400774847919'>
<a name='c6883176400774847919'></a>
<div class="avatar-image-container vcard"><span dir="ltr"><a href="http://www.blogger.com/profile/16072307812436396585" rel="nofollow" onclick="" class="avatar-hovercard" id="av-149-16072307812436396585"><img src="http://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif" width="24" height="35" alt="" class="delayLoad" style="display: none;" longdesc="http://static.flickr.com/100/269086383_e15db506c0_o.jpg" title="Ryan McGinnis">

